column2: "Thanks for helping out with that fruit topper plan! Everyone was really happy with it!"
"...There's one more person I want to help. That person is..."
"...The real Stratos. I inherited the real Stratos's memories. So..."
"I understand why she thinks her Valentine's ability isn't enough. But she won't listen to anything I say."
"I'm sorry to have to ask, but please! Listen to her story... Help the real Stratos!"
